        "eyebrow": "Leadership",
        "name": "Meet Our Founder",
        "designation": "Founder & CEO",
        "short_intro": "<p>A visionary leader shaping the company with elegance, confidence, and a clear long-term direction.</p>",
        "description": "<p>Her journey began with a simple insight: her followers trusted her. Known for her distinctive eyes, lashes, and hair. Youmna regularly received questions about the products she used for her skin care and hair routine.<br/><br/>Recognizing this demand, she launched YOUMI BEAUTY — starting with colored contact lenses and later expanding into lashes and hair extensions. Each product was designed based on her own beauty routine, with a focus on quality, comfort, and visual impact.<br/><br/>Youmna’s involvement in the brand goes beyond her name. She has played a hands-on role in product development, quality control, and creative direction. Her experience with international luxury brands and her understanding of regional beauty preferences allowed her to build a brand that quickly gained traction and credibility.<br/><br/>Today, Youmna Khoury stands as a leading voice in the beauty industry — blending business acumen with social responsibility, and building a brand that is as impactful as it is aspirational.</p>",
        "signature_text": "Founder",
